@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC / Backoffice Operator" as Actor
participant "RouteController" as Ctrl
participant "GetRouteByIdUseCase" as UC1
participant "ListRoutesByAirportUseCase" as UC2
participant "RouteRepository" as Repo
database "Database" as DB

== Get Route Details by ID ==

Actor -> Ctrl : GET /api/routes/{id}
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> UC1 : execute(routeId)
activate UC1

UC1 -> Repo : findByRouteId(routeId)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB : SELECT * FROM routes\nJOIN route_versions WHERE route_id = ?
activate DB
DB --> Repo : route with current version
deactivate DB
Repo --> UC1 : route
deactivate Repo

note right of UC1: Maps Route to RouteResponse\nIncludes current version data\n(distance, estimatedFlightTime)

UC1 --> Ctrl : RouteResponse
deactivate UC1

Ctrl --> Actor : 200 OK (JSON Response)
deactivate Ctrl

== List All Routes from/to a Specific Airport ==

Actor -> Ctrl : GET /api/routes/airport/{iata}
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> UC2 : execute(iataCode)
activate UC2

UC2 -> Repo : findByOriginOrDestination(iataCode)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB : SELECT * FROM routes\nWHERE origin_iata = ? OR destination_iata = ?
activate DB
DB --> Repo : list of routes
deactivate DB
Repo --> UC2 : List<Route>
deactivate Repo

note right of UC2: Maps each Route\nto RouteResponse DTO

UC2 --> Ctrl : List<RouteResponse>
deactivate UC2

Ctrl --> Actor : 200 OK (JSON Array)
deactivate Ctrl
@enduml
